GOLD HAT ADDENDUM

This software is released with one additional expectation (not a legal
requirement, but a moral one):

  Use this to empower, not extract.

Build tools that respect the people who use them. If you fork, extend, or
deploy this software, consider whether your use:

  - Empowers users or extracts from them
  - Teaches while it helps
  - Respects autonomy
  - Builds long-term value

This addendum carries no legal weight. It is an invitation to build
consciously.
